overview: Raven takes a vacation, and leaves her new partner Zara Whites in charge at the office of Catalina Five-0.  Zara crosses paths with a drug dealer the girl detectives have busted in the past, and a mysterious man whose intentions are unknown.  Meanwhile, Raven meets up with some old associates who have amorous intentions.  A Catalina Five-0 adventure.
title: Catalina Five-0: Tiger Shark
